# Railway-side ignore for `railway up`. Mirrors .dockerignore but
# applies during the indexing step before upload.
#
# We only need `site/` — everything else is excluded to (a) keep the
# upload small and fast, (b) avoid broken symlinks in examples/.

**

!site/
!site/**

!railway.json
!.dockerignore

site/_site/
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
